{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"42291-now-i-ve-got-you","title":"Now I've Got You!","description":"One day, Frog catches Wasp. 'Now I've got you!' Frog says. But Wasp sees that Frog is in trouble, too! In a humorous chain of events, each animal is caught and nearly eaten by another, until Wasp comes up with a clever solution to save them all!","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Alisha Berger"],"illustrators":["Mayukh Gosh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/42291-now-i-ve-got-you"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101394/size3/769b9b95f2896b83fb2aa16001371d4f.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101394/size6/769b9b95f2896b83fb2aa16001371d4f.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77945/size6/85a5c7bf2eec373eaedbb3efc435ba10.jpg","text":"2/17","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77946/size6/6fecf81878d33ec6b397cc6cf4a9a07d.jpg","text":"“Now I've got you!” said the Frog.\n“Too bad for you!” said the Wasp.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77928/size6/c9727cf1ed65f1d693a8196e9eb79682.jpg","text":"“Why?” asked Frog \n“Look behind you,” said the Wasp","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77929/size6/bfba51fccd37d8eff094240107f97cbc.jpg","text":"“Now I've got you!” said the Snake.\n“Too bad for you,” said the Frog.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77930/size6/e413bae2d1752619669570134e1fe4cc.jpg","text":"“Why?” asked the Snake.\n“Look behind you,” said the Frog.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77931/size6/80136b42cdc4218bfeb941f8691d00cc.jpg","text":"“Now I've got you!” said the Mongoose.  “Too bad for you,” said the Snake.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77932/size6/77578a04912f2054b5a9497409a660d3.jpg","text":"“Why?” asked the Mongoose. \n“Look behind you,” said the Mongoose.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77933/size6/ee12ad6cf5edfb915953b5159a16be7f.jpg","text":"“Now I've got you!” said the Eagle.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77936/size6/0511bb85307aba4eaaedccccc40d8aff.jpg","text":"\"Frog, let me go and I will save us all!\" yelled the Wasp.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77937/size6/5d23a7718bc50865f5c5fd6b03e4e2ef.jpg","text":"The Frog let go of the Wasp.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77938/size6/835b311a8bc8c7720cf7528c97c7b90d.jpg","text":"The Wasp flew up and stung the Eagle hard on her neck.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77939/size6/0df6a40323a6ff10f306b991b604dcca.jpg","text":"The Eagle let go of the Mongoose.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77940/size6/9ec1600f00c7a44b8d8ad4b9ae55add9.jpg","text":"The Mongoose let go of the Snake.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77941/size6/8d2610ff1a7b4e7624474599b0d9e74b.jpg","text":"The Snake let go of the Frog.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77942/size6/8ea219de9a99f3973017bd21cb0ec3cf.jpg","text":"KER-SPLASH!","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/77943/size6/f2171c64b6b11737f0688d35060bae7c.jpg","text":"Everyone said, \"Thank you, Wasp!\"\nAnd the Alligator thought, \"Now I've got you...\"","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":146}}